Package org.rcsb.mbt.model Description

This package provides classes which define the core data storage containers for the MBT toolkit. Additional sub-packages provide the means to read/write, filter, manipulate, and view this data and its properties.

This is the core MBT package which implements the basic structure component data and property container classes, plus universal structure component identification and iteration mechanisms.
